# Tender Announcement

## Notice of Proposed Tender

### Details

* **Tender Reference Number:** cb-543-5158793
* **Solicitation Number:** W8485-248127/A
* **Publication Date:** 2024-04-17
* **Tender Closing Date:** 2024-05-15T14:00:00
* **Expected Contract Start Date:** 2024-05-16

### Tender Description

The Canadian Department of National Defence is issuing an invitation to submit proposals to procure a tester, material, and permeability item. The successful bidder will be required to deliver one unit of the item to the Canadian Forces Base Trenton by July 2024.

The requested item is detailed as follows:

* **Item 1:** 6635 NSN: 6635-20-000-1576
  + **Part Number:** FX 3300
  + **NCAGE:** SJ483
  + **Unit of Issue:** Ea
  + **Quantity:** 1

### Important Note

Due to the impacts of the COVID-19 pandemic, bidders are strongly encouraged to transmit their bids electronically using the epost Connect service instead of the traditional bid delivery methods.

### Language of Submission

Documents may be submitted in either English or French. Bidders proposing an equivalent or substitute product must indicate the brand name, model, or part number, as well as the NCAGE of the product being offered.

### Miscellaneous

* **Classification:** UNSPC 22101800 Aerial lifts, 25201904 Parachutes
* **Trade Agreements:** Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* **Regions of Opportunity:** World
* **Regions of Delivery:** Ontario (except NCR)
* **End User:** Canadian Forces Base Trenton

### Contact Information

* **Name:** MCpl Poissant-Viau, Audrée
* **Email:** audree.poissant-viau@forces.gc.ca
* **Phone:** 00

### Attachments

Tender notice documents are available at [https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/36040/](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/36040/). Official documents are available in both English and French.
